arm64: perf: set suppress_bind_attrs flag to true

The armv8_pmuv3 driver doesn't have a remove function, and when the test
'CONFIG_DEBUG_TEST_DRIVER_REMOVE=y' is enabled, the following Call trace
can be seen.

